review 1:
I had my birthday party at Laut Cafe, and the owners, Christian and Yulia, and their staff were AMAZING.

I wanted to have a tea party and I requested a special menu of finger bites. The kitchen was extremely creative and crafted a menu that blew away my guests! The space was gorgeous, all my guests raved about how perfect the spot is.

We had such a fun time together, and it was all made possible by the team at Laut Cafe! The service was excellent, the food came out plated to perfection, and they even played a special playlist I created for the party!

They helped me organize a welcome drink for my guests at the last minute, and were so flexible and accommodating.

I'm really happy with their service and I'm obsessed with their beer bread! On their regular menu, I've had their Maultasche, Schupfnudeln with the most delicious sauerkraut and tempeh bits, and Mushroom Toast. All are excellent! Genuinely packed with flavor and cooked with intention.

Thank you Laut Cafe for everything! I can't wait to see you again soon.
